OL,6,FA home-grown Hollywood star has said
OL,7,FLibrary needs to remain open.
OL,9,FThe library where 83-year-old Sir
OL,10,FPatrick Stewart says he nurtured his
OL,11,Flove of reading is threatened with
OL,12,Fclosure as part of a well-publicised
OL,13,Fcost-cutting exercise by Kirklees
OL,14,FCouncil.
