OL,3,CSir Patrick Stewart lends support to
OL,4,Csave childhood library
OL,6,FIn an excerpt from his memoir the Star
OL,7,FTrek and X Men star said ''The
OL,8,FMirfield public library had a very
OL,9,Fgood children's section. And as I got
OL,10,Folder the selection of American
OL,11,Fliterature became my obsession.
OL,12,FHemingway, Fitzgerald, Steinbeck...I
OL,13,Fread them all. You could only take out
OL,14,Ftwo books at a time so I spent part of
OL,15,Fevery Saturday morning at the
OL,16,Flibrary.''
