OL,3,CSir Patrick Stewart lends support to
OL,4,Csave childhood library
OL,6,FCllr Vivien Lees-Hamilton, ward
OL,7,Fcouncillor for Mirfield, said: ''Can
OL,8,Fyou imagine Star Trek without Patrick
OL,9,FStewart? If he hadn't come here it
OL,10,Fmight never have happened. Who knows
OL,11,Fwhat imagination can be fostered here,
OL,12,Fit cannot close.''
OL,14,FIn a bid to save almost #35m, Kirklees
OL,15,FCouncil is proposing to transfer eight
OL,16,Flibraries to ''community management'',
OL,17,Fthey are Honley, Meltham, Marsden,
OL,18,FKirkheaton, Skelmanthorpe, Denby Dale,
OL,19,FMirfield and Shepley.
