OL,3,CSir Patrick Stewart lends support to
OL,4,Csave childhood library
OL,6,FBut the Friends of Mirfield Library
OL,7,Fsaid this would effectively close them.
OL,9,FCynthia Collinson said: ''Repairs,
OL,10,Fmaintenance - lighting, heating - I
OL,11,Fcan't imagine how much it would cost
OL,12,Fto run this 200 year-old building. It
OL,13,Falready needs thousands of pounds of
OL,14,Frepairs. And we are not equipped to
OL,15,Frun it.''
OL,17,FMembers of the library described the
OL,18,Ffacility as a lifeline.
