OL,3,CSir Patrick Stewart lends support to
OL,4,Csave childhood library
OL,6,FRon Powell - who became a member after
OL,7,Fhis wife died in 2019, said: ''I was
OL,8,Fvery depressed, being on my own - and
OL,9,Feven contemplated the worst. And then
OL,10,Fa little brochure came through my
OL,11,Fdoor...that was for a group at the
OL,12,Flibrary.
OL,14,F''Since then I've joined 4 groups in
OL,15,Fthe library - and all of that, really,
OL,16,Fhas saved my life. I just don't want
OL,17,Fto go back to square one.''
OL,19,FIt was a similar story for Diane
OL,20,FKelly, who lost her husband before the
OL,21,Fpandemic.
