OL,3,CSir Patrick Stewart lends support to
OL,4,Csave childhood library
OL,6,FShe said: ''He was always there, to
OL,7,Fhold my hand. I'm partially-sighted,
OL,8,Fand I relied on my husband for
OL,9,Feverything until he died. Then I had
OL,10,Fnothing.
OL,12,F''Now - I have friends to help me
OL,13,Fhere. If I didn't have the library I
OL,14,Fwouldn't have that. I love coming
OL,15,Fhere. I look forward to coming here. I
OL,16,Factually get up on a morning and I
OL,17,Fknow it might sound a bit sad to some
OL,18,Fbut it's my life. It's what I look
OL,19,Fforward to.''
