OL,6,FThe local conservative MP Mark
OL,7,FEastwood said potentially closing the
OL,8,Flibraries was a 'terrible' idea. Asked
OL,9,Fwhat his response was to the fact
OL,10,FKirklees Council blames a lack of
OL,11,Fgovernment funding, he said:
OL,13,F''It's been a shambolic financial
OL,14,Fmismanagement by Kirklees council.
OL,15,FThat's not me saying that - thats the
OL,16,Ffinical auditors.''
