OL,3,CSir Patrick Stewart lends support to
OL,4,Csave childhood library
OL,6,FThe council argues that it has made
OL,7,Fmuch-needed investment in the area for
OL,8,Fmany years. in a statement it said: "A
OL,9,Fproposal to integrate customer service
OL,10,Ffunctions in our libraries and to
OL,11,Fstart talks on transferring some
OL,12,Flibraries to community management was
OL,13,Fapproved at cabinet on 20 February. We
OL,14,Fwill now begin informal engagement on
OL,15,Fthe potential community management of
OL,16,Fsome libraries with a range of key
OL,17,Fstakeholders. The outcome of the
OL,18,Fengagement will be put to cabinet for
OL,19,Fa final decision.
